You are an implementer subagent. Your task is to modify `TransferRequestService::transfer()` in oa-core to support `ai_analysis_config` as a reserved word.

## Context

This is part of a Smart Daily Report Email System. oa-core acts as a proxy between frontend and oa-server. `TransferRequestService::transfer()` forwards requests, extracting "reserved words" (special params) before forwarding, then processing them on the response. We're adding `ai_analysis_config` to support AI analysis via Vertex AI.

`AiAnalysisService` already exists at `D:\project\info-gitlab\oa\oa-core\app\Services\AiAnalysisService.php` with:
- `analyze(string $content, string $systemPrompt): string` — blocking mode
- `analyzeStream(string $content, string $systemPrompt, callable $onChunk, array $history = []): string` — streaming mode

## File to modify

`D:\project\info-gitlab\oa\oa-core\app\Services\TransferRequestService.php`

## Changes Required

### 1. Add `ai_analysis_config` to `reservedWords` array (line 40-43)

Change:
```php
$reservedWords = [
    'decrypt_config', 'encrypt_config', 'update_permission', 'next_replace_filter',
    'hash_filter', 'replace_filter', 'authorize_config', 'intact_columns', 'response_format',
];
```

To:
```php
$reservedWords = [
    'decrypt_config', 'encrypt_config', 'update_permission', 'next_replace_filter',
    'hash_filter', 'replace_filter', 'authorize_config', 'intact_columns', 'response_format',
    'ai_analysis_config',
];
```

### 2. Handle streaming mode with AI analysis (line 97-114)

Replace the existing stream block:
```php
if (!empty($response_format) && $response_format == 'stream') {
    $resp = $this->callBackendApi($action ?: $request->path(), $params, true);
    // convert to stream response
    return response()->stream(function () use ($resp) {
        $body = $resp->toPsrResponse()->getBody();
        $content = '';
        while (!$body->eof()) {
            $bit = $body->read(1);
            $content .= $bit;
            if (substr($content, -2) == PHP_EOL.PHP_EOL) {
                echo $content;
                ob_flush();
                flush();
                $content = '';
            }
        }
    }, $resp->status(), array_merge($resp->headers(), ['X-Accel-Buffering' => 'no']));
}
```

With:
```php
if (!empty($response_format) && $response_format == 'stream') {
    // 如果同时有 ai_analysis_config，需要先拿完整响应再做 AI streaming
    if (!empty($ai_analysis_config) && !empty($ai_analysis_config['system_prompt'])) {
        $resp = $this->callBackendApi($action ?: $request->path(), $params);
        if (!empty($resp['data'])) {
            $respData = &$resp['data'];

            // 解密
            $decrypt_config = empty($respData['decrypt_config']) ? $decrypt_config : array_merge($decrypt_config ?? [], $respData['decrypt_config']);
            if (isset($respData['decrypt_config'])) {
                unset($respData['decrypt_config']);
            }
            if (!empty($decrypt_config)) {
                $respData = DecryptService::app()->decryptData($respData, $decrypt_config, 'response');
            }

            // 提取 AI 输入内容
            $targetField = $ai_analysis_config['target_field'] ?? null;
            $contentForAi = $targetField ? data_get($respData, $targetField, '') : json_encode($respData, JSON_UNESCAPED_UNICODE);
            if (is_array($contentForAi)) {
                $contentForAi = json_encode($contentForAi, JSON_UNESCAPED_UNICODE);
            }

            $systemPrompt = $ai_analysis_config['system_prompt'];
            $history = $ai_analysis_config['history'] ?? [];

            return response()->stream(function () use ($contentForAi, $systemPrompt, $history) {
                AiAnalysisService::app()->analyzeStream(
                    $contentForAi,
                    $systemPrompt,
                    function (string $chunk) {
                        echo 'data: ' . json_encode([
                            'error_code' => 0,
                            'error_msg' => '',
                            'data' => ['type' => 'chat', 'is_finished' => false, 'content' => $chunk],
                        ], JSON_UNESCAPED_UNICODE) . PHP_EOL . PHP_EOL;
                        ob_flush();
                        flush();
                    },
                    $history
                );
                // 结束帧
                echo 'data: ' . json_encode([
                    'error_code' => 0,
                    'error_msg' => '',
                    'data' => ['type' => 'chat', 'is_finished' => true, 'content' => ''],
                ], JSON_UNESCAPED_UNICODE) . PHP_EOL . PHP_EOL;
                ob_flush();
                flush();
            }, 200, [
                'Content-Type' => 'text/event-stream',
                'Cache-Control' => 'no-cache',
                'X-Accel-Buffering' => 'no',
            ]);
        }
    }

    // 原有的 stream 透传逻辑不变
    $resp = $this->callBackendApi($action ?: $request->path(), $params, true);
    return response()->stream(function () use ($resp) {
        $body = $resp->toPsrResponse()->getBody();
        $content = '';
        while (!$body->eof()) {
            $bit = $body->read(1);
            $content .= $bit;
            if (substr($content, -2) == PHP_EOL.PHP_EOL) {
                echo $content;
                ob_flush();
                flush();
                $content = '';
            }
        }
    }, $resp->status(), array_merge($resp->headers(), ['X-Accel-Buffering' => 'no']));
}
```

### 3. Add AI analysis after decryption in non-stream path (after line 126)

After:
```php
if (!empty($decrypt_config)) {
    $respData = DecryptService::app()->decryptData($respData, $decrypt_config, 'response');
}
```

Add:
```php
// AI 分析（解密之后执行，仅当 ai_analysis_config 存在时）
if (!empty($ai_analysis_config) && !empty($ai_analysis_config['system_prompt'])) {
    $targetField = $ai_analysis_config['target_field'] ?? null;
    $outputField = $ai_analysis_config['output_field'] ?? 'ai_analysis';
    $contentForAi = $targetField ? data_get($respData, $targetField, '') : json_encode($respData, JSON_UNESCAPED_UNICODE);

    if (is_array($contentForAi)) {
        $contentForAi = json_encode($contentForAi, JSON_UNESCAPED_UNICODE);
    }

    $aiResult = AiAnalysisService::app()->analyze(
        $contentForAi,
        $ai_analysis_config['system_prompt']
    );
    data_set($respData, $outputField, $aiResult);
}
```

### 4. Add use statement at top

Add `use App\Services\AiAnalysisService;` to the use statements (but it uses ServiceTrait so AiAnalysisService::app() should resolve — but still add the use for clarity).

